c: 2
v: 257
t: "Yalli yeemeneh yan marih Awlaytu catoo kee dacayril, usuk koroosanni diteetak iimaan diifû fanah ken yayyaaqe, koroositeh yan marak Awlaytit keenik Sheytan kee Yallak kalah uqbuddu haanama, usun iimaan diifuk koroosanni diteetâ fanah ken yayyaaqen, woo mari girâ mara usun teetil waarak"